creator: Saint Teresa of Avila
description:
LibriVox recording of The Minor Works of St Teresa of Avila by Saint Teresa of Avila.
Read in English by Ann Boulais
The prayer and Exclamations, or Meditations, of St Teresa of Avila, recorded in honor of the 500th anniversary of the Saint's birth (March 28, 2015). - Summary by Ann Boulais
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
subject: librivox; audiobooks;meditations; Catholic; mysticism
